# Firebase Configuration
# For Vercel: Paste entire service account JSON as a single line
# For local development: Use serviceAccountKey.json file instead

# Option 1: Environment variable (for Vercel deployment)
# Copy your entire Firebase service account JSON and paste it as a single line:
# FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT={"type":"service_account","project_id":"your-project",...}

# Option 2: File-based (for local development)
# Download serviceAccountKey.json from Firebase Console and place in project root
